</section><aside id='sponsorForm'><h2>Become a Sponsor</h2><p>Sponsors will have a table to spread out information and SWAG.</p><p>Without the participation of businesses like yours, the CS Fair will not be considered a success.   Please consider sending a representative to the Fair. This is a great opportunity to see what UVM CS students are up to and to scope out potential future interns and employees for your company.</p> <p>Sponsors will have their company logos posted on the CS Fair website and will be given table space at the Fair to display their company information and SWAG. Sponsors will send at least one representative to see student projects and act as a judge in the $750 ‘Sponsors Choice’ award, and may elect to send a second representative to act as a judge for the $1000 Grand Prize.</p><p>Sponsorship is free, but we do welcome donations of any amount (see below).</p><div id="errors"></div>
